703908f-a.title: Brooklyn: Cropsey Avenue - Bay 37th Street
703908f-a.text:
Cropsey Ave., northward between Bay 37th and Bay 38th Streets. At
the left foreground is 8812 to 8806 Twenty-Fourth Ave. The tall building
in the background is P.S. No. 101 at the S.W. corner of Twenty-Fourth
and Benson Aves.
April 27, 1935.
P. L. Sperr.
NO REPRODUCTIONS.
